        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4411",
        "content": "She was immensely and unfeignedly sorry for him-more sorry than she had ever been for any one in her life, but not sorry enough to deny his words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
